General.Name: Cathay Consolidated Inc
General.Description: Cathay Consolidated, Inc. operates as a contract manufacturer of technical fabrics and finished goods in Taiwan. The company operates through Fabrics and Finished Products divisions. The Fabrics division engages in development and production of thermoplastic polyurethane (TPU) films and technical fabrics. The Finished Products division processes TPU technical fabrics to manufacture a range of inflatable products for various purposes. The company serves its products to aviation, marine, and medical industries, as well as to outdoor retail and wholesale customers. The company was founded in 1982 and is based in Yilan, Taiwan.
